# Attacking Methods & Top 30 Ports

## Common Attack Methods by OSI Layer

| Layer | Attack | Description |
|-------|--------|-------------|
| 7 - Application | SQL Injection, XSS, API Abuse | Malicious input to applications |
| 6 - Presentation | SSL Stripping, Weak Ciphers | Downgrade encryption |
| 5 - Session | Session Hijacking, Fixation | Steal session tokens |
| 4 - Transport | SYN Flood, Port Scanning | Overwhelm resources, discover services |
| 3 - Network | IP Spoofing, BGP Hijack | Fake source IP, redirect traffic |
| 2 - Data Link | ARP Spoofing, MAC Flooding | MITM on local network |
| 1 - Physical | Evil Twin, RF Jamming | Rogue access points, interference |

