## Defense Commands

### Check Open Ports



sudo netstat -tulpn
ss -tulpn

text

### Monitor Network Traffic
sudo tcpdump -i any

text

### Firewall Rules (ufw)
sudo ufw enable
sudo ufw allow 22/tcp
sudo ufw deny 80/tcp

text

### Check ARP Cache (detect spoofing)
arp -a

